title: Rangers 'as bad as I've seen' as Keane revels in Ferencvaros win
subtitle: Rangers were comfortably second-best as they slumped to yet another Europa League defeat, according to victorious Ferencvaros boss Robbie Keane.
full_text: Rangers were comfortably second-best as they slumped to yet another Europa League defeat, according to victorious Ferencvaros boss Robbie Keane.
